data.description: Located on the banks of the Colorado River, Pecan Park is a stunning 311± acre mixed-use development that offers the serenity of river frontage and the convenience of Highway 71 frontage, making this the ideal residential community. Pacesetter homeowners in Pecan Park will have the benefits of full city services and will enjoy large areas of greenbelts, parks, and hike & bike trails. Pecan Park is located on the south side of SH-71 West at Childer's Drive in Bastrop. This location provides 5-minute access to downtown Bastrop and all commercial properties along the main SH-71 corridor and is approximately 30 miles east of downtown Austin and 20 minutes east of Austin-Bergstrom International Airport.
